Class SQLListeners

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mysema.query.sql.SQLListeners
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SQLDetailedListener, SQLListener

    public class SQLListeners
extends Object
implements SQLDetailedListener
    SQLListeners is an SQLListener implementation which dispatches the notifications to a list of SQLListener instances
